    "They chasing each other, completely carefree.",
    "Jonah felt a pang of sadness, realizing that these young ones wouldn't know the wrath of God that he had experienced.",
    "He wondered if they would ever understand the gravity of sin and the need for repentance.",
    "Just then, a young boy approached Jonah, curious about the strange man sitting alone.",
    "\"Hello, sir,\" the child said, eyeing Jonah with fascination."
